# Time Tracker Component Guidelines

## Component Responsibilities

### Main Application
- [TimeTrackerApp.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimeTrackerApp.tsx) - Root component with auth providers and routing logic

### Core Timer Functionality
- [TimerView.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerView.tsx) - Main timer interface with start/stop/metadata flow
- [TimerDisplay.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerDisplay.tsx) - Shows current timer state and elapsed time
- [TimerControls.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerControls.tsx) - Start/stop buttons and controls

### Data Management
- [Activities.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Activities.tsx) - Activity history, editing, and CSV export
- [Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Dashboard.tsx) - Analytics and time tracking insights
- [Settings.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Settings.tsx) - Category management and user preferences

### User Interface
- [Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation between timer tabs and user menu
- [ActivityModal.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/ActivityModal.tsx) - Modal for editing existing activities
- [MetadataForm.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/MetadataForm.tsx) - Form for adding metadata to timer sessions

## Service Dependencies

All time tracker components use:
- [TimeEntryService](mdc:src/services/timeEntryService.ts) - Core time entry CRUD operations
- [CategoryService](mdc:src/services/categoryService.ts) - Category management
- [CSVExportService](mdc:src/services/csvExportService.ts) - Data export functionality

## Context Usage

- **TimerContext**: Used by timer-related components for state management
- **AuthContext**: Used by all components for user authentication state

## Authentication Requirements

All time tracker components require authentication through [AuthGuard](mdc:src/components/shared/AuthGuard.tsx) wrapper in the main app component.
